data.description: Don't miss this amazing opportunity to make money where you live! This beautifully renovated ALL ELECTRIC 4 sided brick home in the sought-after Cascade area has a rare full basement apartment with a separate entry that can serve as a rental producing space. This tastefully designed Very bright home with tons of light features custom touches you will not find anywhere else and checks every box. The rocking chair front porch welcomes you to this one of a kind inviting, open, and spacious floor plan with modern flair flowing effortlessly from the front door is a cozy living room, elegant dining room, and a gourmet eat-in chef's kitchen. The home includes a sunroom off of the kitchen area, expansive deck perfect for family barbecues and a night under the stars, beaming hardwood floors, and thoughtfully designed details throughout. This home combines the best of Intown living as you are close to shopping, parks, the Westside Beltline, Midtown, Downtown, Summerhill, Cascade Springs Nature preserve, John A White Park, Alfred Tup Holmes Golf Courses & McGhee Tennis Center, historic restaurants, West End Breweries, the Atlanta airport, and much more!
